    PAUSE 2 NO-MESSAGE.
    
    CLEAR FRAME f_list_tit  ALL NO-PAUSE.
    CLEAR FRAME f_list_tit2 ALL NO-PAUSE.
    CLEAR FRAME f_list_tit3 ALL NO-PAUSE.

